Deputy President William Ruto’s allies  in Western Kenya have told  the region to rally behind Ruto’s 2022 presidential bid. Speaking in Emuhaya,Vihiga county, the leaders led by  county governor Wilbur Otichillo termed Ruto’s development record  as unmatchable compared to  previous leaders in the region. This as Amani National Congress leader Musalia Mudavadi continued his charm offensive in Central Kenya after hosting former legislators  in his Nairobi residence.   